---
title: Smart 'Buffalo' Turkey Salad with Ranch Dressing
description: This recipe brings all the flavours of wing night, but in a starch-free supper that features tender turkey pieces – an easy-to-cook swap for wings at home. We've even deconstructed the classic wing sides: veggies and ranch, into a delicious, wholesome salad.

